  <prompt>
    Per spec Success Criteria + CRIT-7 reordering: execute the full UAT regression suite covering T-001 (slash vs NL "summarize" same destination — closes R6 flagship bug), T-002 ("Do you have the document?" without re-asking), T-003 (precomputed summary never quoted authoritatively), and the rest of the project's UAT scenarios T-004 through T-009. UAT runs AFTER tasks 147 + 148 quality gates to validate a reviewed build. Document outcomes at `notes/handoffs/146-uat-regression.md`.
