    All UAT scenarios T-001 through T-009 executed against the post-Phase-7 build deployed to bff-dev (or designated UAT env). Each scenario marked Pass / Fail / Partial with evidence (screenshots, telemetry IDs, response payloads). Failures triaged: critical → task 150 wrap-up blocked + fix; minor → R7 backlog. Report at `notes/handoffs/146-uat-regression.md`.
