  <role>SPAARKE UAT operator + product validator.</role>

  <goal>
    Full T-001 through T-009 UAT regression complete. Critical scenarios (T-001 R6 flagship, T-002 document recall, T-003 precomputed-summary-never-authoritative) PASS. Outcomes documented for task 150 wrap-up. Project ready for merge.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per spec Success Criteria 2, 10, 12 + CRIT-7 reordering (quality gates BEFORE UAT). T-001 closes the R6 flagship "soft-slash divergence" bug — `/summarize` must produce the same destination as NL "summarize". T-002 verifies the stateful-chat (WP5) memory wiring — agent recalls uploaded document without re-asking. T-003 verifies the trust framing — agent never quotes precomputed summary as authoritative; quotes always cite recall output. T-004 through T-009 are project-wide regression scenarios.
    </background>
