  <steps>
    <step order="1">Confirm deployed environment is the Phase 7 build with tasks 141 + 142 + 143 changes deployed (verify via build commit SHA).</step>
    <step order="2">Execute T-001 (slash vs NL "summarize" same destination): open chat, upload an NDA, type "summarize this document" → record destination; new session, upload same NDA, type "/summarize" → record destination. Assert same destination.</step>
    <step order="3">Execute T-002 ("Do you have the document?"): upload doc, ask "Do you have the document?" — assert agent responds with file recall confirmation, NOT re-asking for upload.</step>
    <step order="4">Execute T-003 (precomputed-summary-not-authoritative): upload doc with notable specific clause; ask agent to quote that specific clause — assert response cites `recall_session_file` output, NOT the precomputed summary card.</step>
    <step order="5">Execute T-004 through T-009: scenarios from spec Success Criteria + project regression (e.g., NDA routing, patent routing, invoice routing, dedup test, persona binding, evidence precheck).</step>
    <step order="6">Capture per-scenario Pass/Fail/Partial + evidence (deterministic IDs, telemetry trace links, screenshots if available).</step>
    <step order="7">Triage failures: critical → escalate + block task 150; minor → R7 backlog.</step>
    <step order="8">Author report at `notes/handoffs/146-uat-regression.md` with per-scenario outcome table + evidence references + failure triage.</step>
    <step order="9">Update TASK-INDEX.md: task 146 → ✅ (if all critical scenarios pass).</step>
  </steps>

